## ğŸš€ Features

- ğŸ” Fuzzy and prefix-based filename matching
- ğŸ“„ Shows available files when no match is found
- ğŸ§¾ Text-based fallback listing (CLI-friendly)
- âš™ï¸ Custom port and directory support
- âœ… No external dependencies
